summary: 检测 Atlassian Confluence 系统是否存在 CVE-2022-26134 远程代码执行漏洞，通过发送特定请求验证漏洞是否存在并记录相关信息。
summary_en: Detect whether the Atlassian Confluence system has the CVE-2022-26134 Remote Code Execution vulnerability by sending a specific request to verify the existence of the vulnerability and record relevant information.
